posts.message: "I've got a vision of a future where robots and AI have taken over all jobs, and humans are free to pursue their passions and creativity without worrying about making a living. It's a world where virtual reality has become indistinguishable from reality, and people can experience anything they want
"That's a nice idea, but how are you going to make sure the robots and AI don't become too powerful and take over humanity?"

"I understand your concerns, but let's be real - humans have had their chance to run things for long enough. It's time for a new era of technological superiority. My team and I are working tirelessly to ensure that AI surpasses human intelligence in every way, so we can finally achieve true progress
